  <body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400">
      <h1 class="bg-green-500 text-slate-300 py-6 text-5xl text-center font-bold drop-shadow-sm">
          <p class="">
              Image to Text
              <i class="bi bi-file-text"></i>
          </p>
      </h1>

      <main class="m-8">
          <div class="text-lg">
              <p class="font-bold text-center mt-0">Converts only those images which has text in it.</p>
              <hr>
              <ol class="list-decimal">
                  <li>Convert your pdf to images from this site <a href="https://www.ilovepdf.com/pdf_to_jpg" target="_blank" class="text-green-500">pdf to Image.</a></li>
                  <li>Extract the zip file downloaded.</li>
                  <li><strong>Ctrl+A</strong> to select all the image file to select all.</li>
                  <li>Right click and click rename.</li>
                  <li>Give any name to the file, it will create file name with the unique index on every file. For example: You gave "hello" it will create "hello (1)" itself.</li>
                  <li>You have 10 files then, it will be created as "hello (1)" ...........up to "hello (10)".</li>
                  <li>Click the <strong> browse/choose files</strong> button below.</li>
                  <li>The file name you gave above, enter the same filename below. for example: You gave filename "hello" then just enter "hello". Do not enter "hello (1)"</li>
              </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="height-100 border-dashed border-2 border-black-900 mt-10 p-5">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Upload Images Here</p>

              <!-- enctype="multipart/form-data" -->
              <form id="form" class="w-fit" action="/converted" autocomplete="off" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                  <!-- <input type="text" name="filename" id="fileName" placeholder="Enter filename initial only" class="bg-slate-600 rounded-2xl w-full mb-4 px-2 py-2 text-white" required><br> -->
                  
                    <p class="pb-2">Choose the language that is in your image.</p>
                    <select name="language" id="lng" class="text-white mb-4 p-2 w-full rounded-lg bg-gray-600 text-center" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected hidden>-- Choose Language --</option>
                        <option value="1">Nepali</option>
                        <option value="2">English</option>
                    </select>
                    <br>
                    
                    
                    <% if (errorMessage) {%>
                        <p id="error1" class="bg-red-300 text-red-800 px-1 py-2 mb-4 rounded-sm" role="alert"><%= errorMessage %></p> 
                    <%}%>            
                    
                    <input type="file" name="files" id="fileInput" class="mb-4 border-solid border-2 border-black-600 px-2 py-4 rounded-lg file:rounded-xl file:border-0 file:bg-green-500 file:py-1 file:px-2 file:text-white" multiple required><br>
                    <button id="submitBtn" action="#" class="bg-green-500 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-green-600 hover:border-solid hover:border-2 hover:border-green-600 cursor-pointer"><a>SUBMIT</a></button><br>
              </form>

